    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/pavillon-garden-hotel-nha-trang/hotel/nha-trang-vn.html",
    "name": "Pavillon Garden Hotel Nha Trang",
    "detail": "Ok, out of all the choices of hotels in Nha Trang, why would you choose Pavillon Gargen Hotel? Because one, you can walk to the beach in less than 5 minutes. Two, there is awesome street food with fresh sea food, coffee bar, and massage available 50m from the front steps of the hotel, and you don't have to cross a moto filled street. But what really makes this hotel stand out is the staff. Bao, Nhon and Ngan will do just about anything to make you and your visit special. Take the time to stop and talk with them, even if you need to use google translate, it will be worth it! Oh ya, just like all the other review, great breakfast, clean hotel. :)",
