    "name": "Libra Hotel Nha Trang",
    "detail": " What can I say about Libra Hotel Nha Trang except that it is a fabulous find. This is a new hotel with new staff I cannot find anything wrong here. From the moment we walked in we were treated with a friendly welcome. We had booked a room with ‘no window’ which I was a bit nervous about. Turned out it has a small high window with no view. As you are still getting natural light it is fine. It is situated approx 50m from the beach and about 400m from the beach where you can hire a deck chair and umbrella for VND100 per day (yes it is yours for the day!) Exceptional breakfast included in the very reasonable cost. The Seafood Buffet on certain nights is very good value with a great variety of seafood. Mr Canh food and beverage supervisor is wonderful , helpful and caring. The hotel is in a great position, really clean, well positioned pool and great cocktails. Right from reception on the staff are wonderful. Any time I come to Nha Trang again I will certainly book i",
